  "title": "HR Executive | $2,600 | 2 Months Contract | Havelock MRT",
  "description": "<p><strong>💰 Salary: Up to $2,600 per month</strong><br /><strong>🗓️ Contract: 2 Months</strong><br /><strong>⏰ Working Hours: Mon - Fri, 8:45 AM - 6:00 PM</strong><br /><strong>📍 Location: Havelock MRT (Nearest MRT)</strong></p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br />-Assist the HR department in computing and processing critical payroll data with high accuracy.<br />-Manage the effective filing and documentation of confidential HR records.<br />-Update and maintain employee information within our HR systems/databases.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />-Diploma in Human Resources, Business, or a related discipline.<br />-Minimum 1-2 years of relevant experience in processing of HR records / data<br />-Strong attention to detail and ability to handle confidential information discreetly.<br />-Proficiency in basic Microsoft Office functions (Excel, Word).</p><p><br /><strong>Note:</strong> Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
